{"word":"G3569 - τανῦν - tanŷn - tan-oon' - Now","slug":"G3569","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τανῦν</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>tanŷn"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tan-oon'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Now"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C4;&#x03B1;&#x03BD;&#x03C5;&#x0342;&#x03BD;, &#x03C4;&#x03B1;&#x0300; &#x03BD;&#x03C5;&#x0342;&#x03BD; - tanun  ta nun</b> - <i>tan-oon', tah noon</i><p/>From neuter plural of <a href=\"#/G3588\">G3588</a> and <a href=\"#/G3568\">G3568</a>; <i>the</i> things <i>now</i>, that is, (adverb) <i>at present:</i> - (but) now."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3568\">G3568</a>, <a href=\"#/G3570\">G3570</a>"}]}